thought.text: Let me get the complete dataset to show all results:

data.query:
SELECT 
  `Product Name`,
  ROUND(`Our Price`, 2) as Our_Price,
  ROUND(`Competitor Price`, 2) as Competitor_Price,
  ROUND(`Price Difference`, 2) as Price_Difference,
  CASE 
    WHEN `Price Difference` > 0 THEN CONCAT('We are $', CAST(ROUND(ABS(`Price Difference`), 2) AS STRING), ' MORE expensive')
    WHEN `Price Difference` < 0 THEN CONCAT('We are $', CAST(ROUND(ABS(`Price Difference`), 2) AS STRING), ' LESS expensive')
    ELSE 'Same price'
  END as Competitive_Analysis
FROM `bigquery_pricing_analysis.analysis` 
ORDER BY `Price Difference` DESC
